OL,5, Train drivers at Avanti West Coast will
OL,6, see their fee for an overtime shift    
OL,7, increase to #600 following a deal      
OL,8, between the company and union Aslef.   
OL,10,FAvanti said it hoped offering more     
OL,11,Fattractive terms to its drivers to work
OL,12,Fextra shifts would make its services   
OL,13,F"more reliable and resilient".-        
OL,15,FThe company has faced criticism over   
OL,16,Fcancellations, delays and poor service.
OL,18,FAn Aslef source confirmed that Avanti's
OL,19,Foffer was accepted by union bosses.    
